      <div class="- topic/div ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">The common alarm is active if at least one alarm is active
that effect the common alarm. It is indicated by the red common alarm
LED and the audible alarm. The common alarm is only resolved when
all other alarms that effect the common alarm are cleared.</p>
